    "description": "Join the ranks of history's greatest generals and redefine the outcomes of the most significant battles of the Napoleonic era. All it takes is a strategic mind and the will to command. Dive into our game now on Steam and lead your troops to glory!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/0713cb93b6a97d952892d4591658f3ce.avif?t=1727941200\" width=616 height=315 /></span><br>Dive into 6 detailed campaigns each representing a pivotal phase of the Napoleonic Wars — from Preussisch-Eylau in 1807 to the battles of 1814. Each campaign offers a series of battles that shaped the course of history, bringing over 150 missions to your screen.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/d47ee28e3363e8fd40af10bfda920337.avif?t=1727941200\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/bc4db9dee89f7fe2d0a998ac983e9d15.poster.avif?t=1727941200\" width=616 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/bc4db9dee89f7fe2d0a998ac983e9d15.webm?t=1727941200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/bc4db9dee89f7fe2d0a998ac983e9d15.mp4?t=1727941200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each mission showcases a historical battlefield with meticulously positioned army regiments, bringing military history battle maps directly to your screen. Historical accuracy meets tactical gameplay here, where the positioning and terrain play as much a role as your regiments and decisions.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/25c4710007f299a1b980dbbf5a0f59d8.avif?t=1727941200\" width=616 height=431 /></span><br>We've meticulously recreated the authentic design of Napoleonic Wars-era army regiments, complete with historically accurate uniforms and capabilities. It's not just about classifying units as infantry, cavalry, or artillery; it’s about the unique history of each specific regiment, which can significantly impact their role on the battlefield.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/741a32d4efb4d179c62d0dbf393d55a4.avif?t=1727941200\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/e9efa4afe88d4c5186c5ded2e42f41cf.poster.avif?t=1727941200\" width=616 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/e9efa4afe88d4c5186c5ded2e42f41cf.webm?t=1727941200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/e9efa4afe88d4c5186c5ded2e42f41cf.mp4?t=1727941200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>To provide full immersion of battlefield command, we’ve combined turn-based elements like hexagonal grid movement with the simultaneous actions characteristic of RTS. This results in gameplay with a more deliberate pace, where quick reflexes aren’t essential—only a keen strategic mind. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/aa1bae767190a9ba706ac705f6b4ef77.avif?t=1727941200\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/def4f4df202e7d3c947d96759ada8eb6.poster.avif?t=1727941200\" width=616 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/def4f4df202e7d3c947d96759ada8eb6.webm?t=1727941200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096190/extras/def4f4df202e7d3c947d96759ada8eb6.mp4?t=1727941200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Leverage historical formations like squares, columns, or skirmish lines to gain tactical advantages on the battlefield. Transform your units dynamically to suit the unfolding tactical scenario. With a system designed to minimize randomness, predict the outcome of your strategies and attacks with high accuracy, similar to traditional tabletop wargaming.",
